{"body": "Note also that for single-attribute `composed_of` usage (e.g. `Money`), this can be achieved via a customer serializer:\n\n``` ruby\nclass MoneySerializer\n  def dump(money)\n    money.value\n  end\n\n  def load(value)\n    Money.new(value)\n  end\nend\n\nclass Fare\n  serialize :price, MoneySerializer.new\nend\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6353595", "created_at": "2012-06-15T10:26:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6743#issuecomment-6353595", "updated_at": "2012-06-15T10:26:23Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6743, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonleighton", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/2940bc7d4506f3e099e3dcc32a412b98?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F798cebccb32617ad94123450fd137104.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/received_events", "gravatar_id": "2940bc7d4506f3e099e3dcc32a412b98", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jonleighton", "type": "User", "id": 1979, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonleighton/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e2d0bbd354364b900e149"}, "id": 6353595, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6743"}
